column5: Was at a lake with no Muskies   , so whattya do? Bass fish! It started out good and we had some fun, all released,    some big ones caught and we lost some giants, they were loving the frogs in the slop and even some spinnerbaits.  Lots of fun,last year I got a couple back to back nickles, not so this year, but still some decent fish
Nice Matt I thought you would have used 6" sledge and a small egg head spinner bait for them bait fish
Wow, some serious big mouths in there!
Hey, not bad for a Sens fan! HH
Great day you had,I"ll be targeting large mouth this weekend myself!!!!!!!. I now know where there hiding.
